Segmentation of the fiber optics market based on type includes single-mode fiber optics and multi-mode fiber optics. Single-mode fiber optics are primarily utilized for long-distance communication as they have the capability to transmit data over extended distances with minimal signal loss. Conversely, multi-mode fiber optics find common applications in shorter distances. The application segment of the market covers various industries such as telecom, oil & gas, military & aerospace, healthcare, BFSI, IT & telecom, among others, each driving the demand for fiber optic solutions. Geographically, North America and Europe are key regions in the market owing to technological advancements and the presence of major market players.

